First District.

Nilson Brothers, complainant, v. Nathan Grossman et al., appellees, on appeal of Nilson Brothers and G. L. Clausen, trading as Clausen and Company, appellants.Gen. No. 37,818.Heard in the first division of this court for the first district at the October term, 1934.Opinion filed April 15, 1935.Rehearing denied April 29, 1935.John E. Owens and Edwin J. Nunn, for appellants; Clyde C. Fisher, of counsel. Sherman M. Booth, for certain appellees. Mr. Presiding Justice O’Connor

delivered the opinion of the court.
